LAMMPS (3 Mar 2020)
# Alpha
clear
units		real
dimension 3
boundary        p p p
atom_style	charge
newton on
read_data       OOH_6.lmp
  orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (32.808 17.78 2.473)
  4 by 2 by 1 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  59 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.0036255 secs

timestep 0.25

# ---------- Define Interatomic Potential ---------------------
